SCM1R.RG.long_name: AS Siguldas Ciltslietu Un Maksligas Apseklosanas Stacija
SCM1R.RG.summary: AS Siguldas Ciltslietu Un Maksligas Apseklosanas Stacija produces and supplies breeding bull semen in the Republic of Latvia. It also provides milk testing services; and other breeding related services, such as consultations on issues of cattle breeding, feeding and keeping, evaluation of cow exterior, artificial insemination of cows, and initial processing of the supervisory data. In addition, the company engages in making of milk analyses and milk recording data processing activities, as well as organizes animal breeding. AS Siguldas Ciltslietu Un Maksligas Apseklosanas Stacija was founded in 1957 and is based in Sigulda, the Republic of Latvia.
